##  -----------  -------  -------  ----  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
##  2017-Nov-11  Initial   0.2.0   ADCL  Initial version
##  2018-Dec-14  Initial   0.2.0   ADCL  Add an option (by commenting/un-commenting) to boot a near-bare-metal
##                                       timer test binary
